# vhs capture-harness transient GIF byproduct (vhs requires an Output; we only
# commit the screenshot PNG, not the GIF). Tapes write the GIF into the hidden
# .gifcache/ subdir so the vhs dir listing stays clean. See testdata/vhs/README.md.
testdata/vhs/.gifcache/
testdata/vhs/*.gif
